<table border=0 cellspacing=1 cellpadding=1>
	<tr>
		<td valign=middle align=left width=22><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=1 width=20 border=0></td>
		<td valign=middle align=right class="header">Viewing A Message</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2"><hr size="1"></td></tr>
	<tr>
    <td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text">To view an intranet message 
      or email.</td>
  </tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the <strong>Messaging</strong> 
      link from the main menu to view the messages in the Inbox. The <em>Message 
      Listing</em> will show <em>From</em>, <em>Subject</em>, <em>Unread</em>, 
      <em>@</em> (Attachment) and <em>Received</em> (Date & Time).</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the message's subject to view 
      the message body.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">3.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">Inside the message, click on the <strong>Previous</strong> 
      or the<strong> Next</strong> button to navigate to other messages sequentially.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">4.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the <strong>Reply</strong> 
      button to reply to the sender, the<strong> Reply All </strong>button to 
      reply to all the recipients and the <strong>Forward </strong>button to forward 
      to new recipients.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">5.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the <strong>Delete</strong> 
      button to delete a message.The message will be sent to the Trash folder. 
      To permanently delete messages, click on the <strong>Empty</strong> link 
      beside Trash folder.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">6.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the <strong>Save Contacts</strong> 
      button to save all email recipients and the sender's email addresses into 
      the personal contacts.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">7.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">To view messages from the other folders, 
      click on the Folder Name under the folder listing.</td>
	</tr>
</table>
